{"tid":823201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐港共軍部隊進行防颱風演練  特區政府有需要時即出動","createTime":"2018-09-16T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:54:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fa84154a2dcf4abed6ae2caed09f5817e37d6dca","tid":823201,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"中新社香港9月16日電 據解放軍駐香港部隊16日消息，在強颱風「山竹」來襲之前，駐港部隊除自身防護以外，也加班進行了防颱風演練。<br />\n<br />\n駐港部隊的艦艇全部駛離昂船洲，前往避風港拋錨，以躲避「山竹」的正面衝擊，直升機也轉場避風。駐港部隊並在野外駐訓場加緊固定裝備物資，以防止強風對裝備造成破壞。<br />\n<br />\n除了自身防護，駐港部隊也加班進行防颱風演練，確保在特區政府需要的時候，能夠迅速出動，最大限度挽回人民群眾生命財產損失。<br />\n<br />\n駐港部隊表示，無論「山竹」來勢有多猛，駐港部隊都時刻準備，只要上級一聲令下，解放軍就會全力以赴前往救援。(完)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20180916/28206928.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F28206928.html&d=LapXABF7ezdQnoimPfG6IgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d0c7b6a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20180916/28206928.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b973584f4ef7001a2139bfa3e72eb0d4a5551ed","tid":823201,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"市民明天記得準時返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6799b0272d09f3ebe9c6cdf197dc157b9ede22","tid":823201,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"喂，你要loop都早啲loop啦，下晝已經睇過幾次"},{"pid":"216769f1adbd3fc90ce0d384e67f1e28f90351ff","tid":823201,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6799b0272d09f3ebe9c6cdf197dc157b9ede22","tid":823201,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:51:25.000Z","msg":"喂，你要loop都早啲loop啦，下晝已經睇過幾次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"喺香土睇呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fb6291f3382035913cedfd28ade17c750e2982","tid":823201,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":